{"tid":1334188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察帶頭搞網絡欺凌消防員","createTime":"2019-07-20T04:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T04:30:03.000Z","uid":203952,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9591de3c040ff9757f1e6a9abdf04180fcd3da05","tid":1334188,"uid":203952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"【#請廣傳】<br />\n<br />\n警察是磨心嗎？但警察卻帶頭搞網絡欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n消防員一家於油塘連儂牆貼memo紙為示威者打氣，竟立即遭黑警拍照「點相」，照片其後被發佈至Facebook 「順利邨紀律部隊宿舍」群組內。<br />\n<br />\n群組成員把一家三口的資料迅速「起底」，更打電話糾纏妻子，並呼籲群組成員到其工作地點騷擾她。<br />\n<br />\n事後妻子坦言對行為感到恐懼，日後會减少外出。<br />\n<br />\n而7月初，警方網罪科拘捕8名涉嫌「起底」披露黑警惡行，的個人資料及其家人私隱。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察，知法犯法。警局已經幫槍頭對準市民，故我們必須自救，宣其惡行！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJoGvmJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJoGvmJ.png&h=3e2bc288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2811268295612444?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2787894407949833%2Fposts%2F2811268295612444%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbnobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=e00d4003\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2811268295612444?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支持消防員，反黑警</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad77f39034e4f5f1e51d9e2ae270e49e27253305","tid":1334188,"uid":238051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>保障手足 指出偽警</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極不建議自行逮捕</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但必須當場指出冒警人士</span><br />\n撲滅罪行 你我有責<br />\n<br />\n【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih